{"tid":1657950,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家開始明點解晚清要比人八國聯軍圍毆","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:23:52.000Z","uid":308233,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"144edc4c1e16a43aa9913eb8fcd1a9de1f7cd235","tid":1657950,"uid":308233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"細個聽果陣都覺得晚清幾慘<br />\n甚至有d可憐佢<br />\n但係而家<br />\n我開始覺得佢地係抵撚死嘅<br />\n中國人幾千年嚟都係咁戇鳩<br />\n自大到仆街<br />\n但係又唔打得<br />\n乜都要人遷就<br />\n就係唔遷就人<br />\n人地話佢唔啱<br />\n佢就話翻人唔啱<br />\n從來唔思考下自己嘅問題<br />\n人地好好地想同佢傾<br />\n佢就串到仆街<br />\n一係就傾掂數跟住反口<br />\n<br />\n一路打呢編野都打到我燥<br />\n中共真係正臭雞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快撚d滅國<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c871fc86d5836766a9a970264abc6f1989d6ad","tid":1657950,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3afc63841163009aab7d2cf6ed7098b5f11bd09d","tid":1657950,"uid":316103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"話佢臭雞真係好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51def3d2d5baae494db8cc0f9760117fa62979ca","tid":1657950,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"出議反議正仆街"},{"pid":"aefc44fc3c7f2fd68faf806e329f91b1fed0e8ab","tid":1657950,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}